summary: This document is a financial alert from Deutsche Bank Private Bank regarding Neptune, LLC, which is associated with various aliases and appears on the OFAC Specially Designated Nationals list. The alert includes details about the entity's registration and associated vessels, indicating potential compliance issues.
keyFacts: Neptune, LLC is associated with multiple aliases including SEAPRIDE and ASTANEH.
The alert was generated on October 2, 2013, indicating compliance concerns.
The entity appears on the OFAC Specially Designated Nationals list as of September 26, 2013.
The document includes a tracking ID and reporting ID for internal reference.
There are confidentiality clauses regarding the handling of the information contained in the document.
